<topic id="associate-ant-validation-scenario">
  <title>Associate a Validation Scenario</title>
  <body>
    <p>You are able to validate Ant build files using a validation scenario. To create a validation
      scenario, select <uicontrol><image href="../img/bt_configure_validation_scenario.png"
          id="image_bfh_sf5_5n"/>Configure Validation Scenario(s)...</uicontrol> from the
          <uicontrol><image href="../img/bt_validation20.png" id="image_y4w_3pb_2r"
        />Validation</uicontrol> toolbar drop-down list or the <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Validate</uicontrol>
      </menucascade> menu.</p>
  </body>
</topic>
